t, warrior only, secondary slot, ac 38, str/dex/sta 8, 65 hp, focus effect &quot;furious bash 2 &quot;. Anyone know what this is and whether its ever worth equipping? <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=366288">Quakr's profil</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=varaho1>Varaho1</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/white_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 1194<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/17/02 12:07:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4668.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   No</span><hr size=1> Only furious bash 2? No way. <br>
<br>
I am willing to bet 30% of your aggro is coming from the offhand in your dual wield setup. Giving up DPS and aggro just for stats is silly.<br>
<br>
BTW from all indications it is not a true focus effect, not that it maters really. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/bthesteelwarrior.showUserPublicProfile?gid=raaj>Raaj</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>will kick your @$$</span><br>  Posts: 560<br> <font color=#FF0000>(12/17/02 2:15:00 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebunker.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4668.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: No</span><hr size=1> Furious Bash II<br>
